hopobject.body: Languages sirun erexaneri nkarner 2015 Her appointment also comes at a critical moment for the Obama administration as it wrestles with the shutdown of some government services and the imminent threat of default. Having largely discounted this threat, dismissed yesterday by the IMF as a low-probability tail risk, markets are beginning to take it seriously, with share prices drifting lower and the yield on very short-dated Treasury bills rising precipitously. Yellen is being presented as a rare example of stability and continuity amid all the political turmoil.
